<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

  <Paragraph>  
This sample creates a template document that contains different kinds of Hyperlinks, and lets the user to modify the content of those Hyperlinks and save the result into a new document. 
  </Paragraph>

  <Paragraph>
Below is the illustration of the output document generated using Essential DocIO with various hyperlinks.
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph TextAlignment ="Center">
<Image Source="Images\sample.png" Height="530" Stretch="None"/> 
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">Features:</Paragraph> 
<List>
			<ListItem><Paragraph>Supports to create, modify and retrieve the Hyperlinks.</Paragraph></ListItem>   
           <ListItem><Paragraph>Supports Web, E-mail, Image, File and Bookmark Hyperlink.</Paragraph></ListItem>   
</List>

</FlowDocument>